      <h2 feature__item-title="">Peierls Instability</h2>
      <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
        These notes are on the Peierls Instability, a phenomenon that ensures that simple pictures of metals do not work in 1D. Contains use of second quantised operators throughout, with linear response ideas stated.
